Similar in all ways to "edit profile" except:

Launches an editor to edit your profile.  Which editor is launched depends on
how you access Monolith..  If you telnet, the pico-editor is launched.  If
you're on the CLient, the editor will vary, depending on which CLient you use.
 
yNotew:g  Editor editing of your profile allows you more than 7 lines, but please
don't have a 30 screen profile..
